1
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:47,639
Don't! Don't! Don't!

2
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:53,320
Are you really going to kill him?

3
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:54,000
Phkin!

4
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:55,559
Please calm down!

5
00:00:55,559 --> 00:00:57,039
Calm down, dear.

6
00:00:58,119 --> 00:00:59,840
Nai's life

7
00:01:00,039 --> 00:01:02,159
must be paid for with his!

8
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,639
But before he dies

9
00:01:05,639 --> 00:01:07,760
he's going to suffer
in absolute agony

10
00:01:08,679 --> 00:01:10,360
To pay for what he did
to Pakinai.

11
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:16,320
Forget about eating.

12
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:18,480
Pick up the axe.

13
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:23,280
I said, pick up the axe!

14
00:01:37,239 --> 00:01:40,239
Chop all of this firewood.

15
00:01:43,119 --> 00:01:46,199
I told you to chop all
of this firewood!

16
00:01:46,559 --> 00:01:49,280
Don't you understand
plain language?!

17
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:08,719
What the hell are you doing?

18
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,639
I told you he's never
done this before.

19
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,280
He doesn't know how.

20
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:25,960
What the hell are you doing?!

21
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,719
Have you ever worked a
hard day in your life?

22
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:30,000
What are you even good for?

23
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:32,079
Or is the only thing
you know how to do.

24
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:33,639
tricking men into falling for you

25
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:36,000
and then tossing them aside?

26
00:03:05,679 --> 00:03:07,360
Impossible.

27
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:13,159
What's impossible, Khun Mavin?

28
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,840
Looking at all this CCTV footage

29
00:03:16,239 --> 00:03:17,039
everyone else is on it.

30
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:18,960
But Venus and

31
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:22,079
Saturn are nowhere to be seen.

32
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,800
What's so strange about that?

33
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,679
The two brothers probably

34
00:03:25,679 --> 00:03:28,159
just agreed not to show up.

35
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:30,760
Wait a minute.

36
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,639
Wait for what?

37
00:03:33,119 --> 00:03:34,480
There's a gap in the footage.

38
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:36,559
It's like the cameras

39
00:03:36,559 --> 00:03:37,239
just stopped recording.

40
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,039
Does that mean

41
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,199
the cameras malfunctioned?

42
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:41,840
No.

43
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:44,159
It's more likely someone

44
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:45,480
intentionally disabled them.

45
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,360
What now, Khun Pakin?

46
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,199
Go fetch some water.

47
00:04:21,159 --> 00:04:23,119
Are you not going to
let me rest at all?

48
00:04:23,599 --> 00:04:24,159
No.

49
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,079
Fine!

50
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,639
Wait.

51
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,719
Khun Pakin?

52
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,320
The well is that way.

53
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:45,519
You could've just told me nicely.

54
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:01,880
Kin

55
00:05:04,039 --> 00:05:05,079
I knows

56
00:05:05,559 --> 00:05:06,719
and understands.

57
00:05:07,599 --> 00:05:09,840
I've watched the
two of you grow up.

58
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,960
I know how much
you both struggled

59
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:15,239
to get to where you are today.

60
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:19,440
But Kin, you have to understand

61
00:05:20,559 --> 00:05:25,599
you cannot fight fire with fire.

62
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,960
Aunt Tammy

63
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,440
I'd give you anything

64
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,719
you ask for.

65
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,880
But not this,
Please let me have this.

66
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,320
I have to avenge my brother.

67
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:47,320
Kin,
how is this going to end, my dear?

68
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,800
How will it end?

69
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:52,719
Does someone have to die?

70
00:05:52,719 --> 00:05:53,320
Huh?

71
00:05:53,719 --> 00:05:56,280
Is that what it
takes to satisfy you?

72
00:05:56,719 --> 00:05:58,199
And what good will that do?

73
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:03,199
What will become of your future

74
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,039
Tell me.

75
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,480
You have a point, Mavin.

76
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:20,199
Madame, do you think it's possible.

77
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:21,360
that this has something to do

78
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,519
with you handing over

79
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:23,920
the top executive position

80
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:27,320
to Khun Venus and Khun Saturn?

81
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,559
It's highly possible.

82
00:06:29,559 --> 00:06:32,119
But if someone is trying to
get rid of my grandsons

83
00:06:32,119 --> 00:06:33,719
to stop them from
taking the position

84
00:06:35,519 --> 00:06:38,679
who do you think
that person could be?

85
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:44,840
It's likely someone close to us.

86
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,719
But to be absolutely sure

87
00:06:48,079 --> 00:06:51,280
I need to find evidence to prove it.

88
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,840
Alright, here we are.

89
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,159
This room is perfect.

90
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,320
No one else is using it.

91
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,639
So,

92
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,320
for tonight.

93
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,400
you'll sleep here.

94
00:07:11,239 --> 00:07:12,360
And most importantly

95
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:17,280
don't even think
about running away.

96
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:19,519
Just like Pakin warned you.

97
00:07:20,039 --> 00:07:20,880
Understood?

98
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:24,079
Mmm.

99
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:25,719
Alright, I'm heading to bed.

100
00:07:25,719 --> 00:07:26,519
Wait, Miss Tammy.

101
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:27,400
What now?

102
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,159
You're such a handful.

103
00:07:29,159 --> 00:07:31,719
Always asking for something.
What is it?

104
00:07:31,719 --> 00:07:32,360
Um...

105
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,679
Oh.

106
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,119
I know what this is about.

107
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:41,559
If you're going to ask
for this and that

108
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,760
Let me tell you right now

109
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,920
you're not getting it

110
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:50,639
This isn't a five-star hotel.

111
00:07:51,039 --> 00:07:53,840
This is a penitentiary.

112
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,199
Your personal prison.

113
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:01,280
But wait, Miss Tammy.

114
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:04,320
I know exactly what
my status is here.

115
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:07,119
I'm here as Khun Pakin's prisoner

116
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:11,559
Whether I live or die
is entirely up to him.

117
00:08:11,559 --> 00:08:13,440
Well, good that you understand.

118
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:15,599
If you understand, then great

119
00:08:15,599 --> 00:08:16,960
That's settled. Good night.

120
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,399
I'm going to sleep.

121
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,720
Wait, please!

122
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,199
What is it with you?!

123
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:21,760
It's just..

124
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,600
If I have to live with a monster

125
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,920
I'd at least like to know who he is.

126
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,800
Could you tell me the story

127
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,840
of Khun Pakin?

128
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,159
Why do you need to know?

129
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,760
Additional photographic evidence

130
00:08:49,199 --> 00:08:51,319
Khun Venus's room.

131
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,479
Everything looks
perfectly in order.

132
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:58,840
Nothing out of the ordinary.

133
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,960
No signs of a struggle.
